flavor = "In combat, a ruthless machine, but in peace barely even says anything.
Trained in the use of Exokirasso. As an Agarthian, she is the only member capable of activating their devices.
She possesses a symbiote which regulates bodily functions and will administer painkillers, atropine and stimulants into her bloodstream, making her immune to chemical weapons and most biological hazards.
She also possesses a \"Smart Goo\" suit with many benefits, but is vulnerable radiation and electronic warefare.
She is 18 years old in 2025, or 1711 in Agarthian calendar. Making her military career 12 years long, as Agarthians are born (or manufactured) fully developed as adults.
Her Agarthian signature is petrichor or geosmin, an identifying quality that Katherine seems to pick up mysteriously.
Her military training tattoo doesn't state a division, like most Agarthian soldiers, only depicting the emblem of Agartha."
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://cd1xjw6enffjq"
